# Design

## Stack

- Tailwind CSS 4 with CSS variables for tokens
- shadcn/ui components in `components/ui/`
- Icons: `lucide-react`

## Tokens

- Use semantic classes: `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `border-border`, `text-muted-foreground`
- Brand colors come from org `brand_kits` at export time; app chrome uses default theme
- Spacing: Tailwind scale (4px base); rounded corners via `rounded-md` / `rounded-lg`

## Typography

- Headings: clear hierarchy (`text-2xl font-semibold` page titles)
- Body: `text-sm` or `text-base` for content areas
- Monospace for IDs, debug, code snippets only

## Components

- Cards for deck/project list items
- Tabs for editor panels (content / notes / preview)
- Buttons: primary for main CTA, outline for secondary, ghost for toolbar actions

## Slide preview

- 16:9 aspect ratio container
- Layout-specific templates mirror export output
- Respect brand kit colors in preview when `apply_branding` is true

## Do not

- Raw hex in components (use CSS variables or Tailwind theme)
- One-off spacing values outside the scale without reason
